description: This stunning brownstone is located on the most desirable street on the East side of South Boston, offering timeless curb appeal, and lives like a single-family home. The renovated 4+ bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home spans 1,705 sf across 3 floors and features a private entrance, exclusive roof rights, and a deck off of the kitchen.  The inviting open-concept first floor boasts high ceilings, original moldings, exposed brick, and abundant natural light. The updated kitchen features granite countertops, an oversized island & stainless steel appliances. Cozy living and dining areas are highlighted by a decorative marble fireplace and a half bath completes this level.  Each of the 4 well-appointed bedrooms have a large custom closet, while the front bedrooms offer oversized bow windows for extra light. A 5th room on the 3rd floor can serve as a nursery, workout room, or a home office. Enjoy ample storage, in-unit laundry, and central air throughout.
